File: A burning candle. eNCA JOHANNESBURG - Eskom has ramped up power cuts to Stage 6 from 8pm. Stage 6 will last until 5am on Sunday. READ: Eskom named newsmaker of the year The power utility says Stage 6 might continue on Sunday night. Eskom says the increased blackouts are needed to replenish emergency generation reserves. South Africa has been experiencing rolling power cuts since the start of the year.